{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_05_02",
  "title": "サニーピース 05 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "友ちゃんはテレビや雑誌が大好きで\nアイドルとかおしゃれとかいろんなことに詳しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomo-chan loved TV and magazines‚\nand she knew so much about idols and fashion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.875510311100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "世の中には楽しいことが沢山あるんだよって\n私に教えてくれた、楽しいことの師匠なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She taught me that there are so many\nfun things in the world. She's my \"Master of Fun.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0688433964,
      "endTime": 16.7963717777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "楽しいことの師匠か……\nさくらにとっていい出会いだったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A Master of Fun‚ huh…\nIt sounds like a wonderful encounter for you‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9897048631,
      "endTime": 23.3879814782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "素敵なお友達ね。アイドルが好きなら、さくらちゃんが\nアイドルになった時は喜んでくれたんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a lovely friend. If she likes idols‚\nwouldn't she be thrilled that you became one?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5613134699,
      "endTime": 33.391449578300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだね\n生きていたら、きっと喜んでくれたんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I suppose so.\nIf she were still alive‚ I'm sure she would have been.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5781163213,
      "endTime": 41.3781163213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "生きていたら？　じゃあ、その子は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If she were still alive? You mean‚ that girl…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5847830452,
      "endTime": 46.502220884699994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "友ちゃんは重い病気で、出会った時にはもう\n私と同じように余命宣告されていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomo-chan had a serious illness. When we met‚\nshe had already been given a terminal diagnosis‚ just like me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7155542371,
      "endTime": 55.035554695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "いつも明るく振る舞ってたけど、友ちゃんも本音では\n死ぬのが凄く怖かったはずで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She always acted bright‚ but deep down‚\nshe must have been so scared of dying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2422213235,
      "endTime": 63.6822216669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そういうところも私と同じだから、お互いの気持ちが\nよく分かって、より仲良くなれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were the same in that way‚ so we understood\neach other's feelings well and became even closer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8888882953,
      "endTime": 71.05446646989999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二人が出会ってから、数年後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― A few years after they met",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0411330222,
      "endTime": 73.3411330222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 73.3411330222
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 73.3411330222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん！　大変だよ！　大変なんだよ！\nこれを見て！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan! This is big! It's huge!\nLook at this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2077994346,
      "endTime": 78.8211322306,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4799.999491400002,
          "startTime": 79.007798926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 79.007798926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "これは……星見まつりのチラシ？\nそっかあ、もう夏祭りの時期なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this… a flyer for the Hoshimi Festival?\nI see‚ it's already time for the summer festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.007798926,
      "endTime": 87.7577987352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9444653828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "えーと……星見市出身のアイドルによる特別ライブ……\nへえ、お祭りの会場にアイドルが来るんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see… A special live by idols from Hoshimi City…\nOh‚ an idol is coming to the festival grounds.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9444653828,
      "endTime": 100.8770280201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだよ！　私の推しのアイドルが\n星見まつりでライブをやるんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! My favorite idol\nis going to perform at the Hoshimi Festival!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0836948394,
      "endTime": 106.9770233154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1836897532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo003.m4a",
      "text": "この体じゃ、東京のライブなんて一生行けないと\n思ってたけど……地元のお祭りなら行けるよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought with this body‚ I'd never get to go to a live in Tokyo‚\nbut… I can definitely make it to a local festival!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1836897532,
      "endTime": 114.87701937349999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo004.m4a",
      "text": "と言う訳でさくらちゃん！\n星見まつり、一緒に行こう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Sakura-chan!\nLet's go to the Hoshimi Festival together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0836861927,
      "endTime": 119.1170159656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 119.3170159656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "友ちゃんと一緒にお祭り……いいね！　私も行きたい！\n二人で流星群を見に行こうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Going to a festival with you… sounds great! I want to go too!\nLet's go see the meteor shower together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3170159656,
      "endTime": 128.2908707936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo005.m4a",
      "text": "決まりだね！\nさくらちゃんと行く夏祭り、楽しみだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a deal!\nI'm so looking forward to the summer festival with you~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4975374221,
      "endTime": 133.964209175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後、星見まつり当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― A few weeks later‚ the day of the Hoshimi Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8642183303,
      "endTime": 136.16421858459998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1642185846
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1642185846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo006.m4a",
      "text": "ごほごほ……ごめんね、さくらちゃん……\n一緒にお祭りに行くって約束したのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cough‚ cough… I'm sorry‚ Sakura-chan…\nEven though we promised to go to the festival together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0308865229,
      "endTime": 150.0841905275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "熱が出たんじゃ仕方ないよ\n今日は私も病院に残るから、二人で夜までお喋りしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be helped if you have a fever.\nI'll stay at the hospital too‚ so let's talk until tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2975236892,
      "endTime": 158.35752391810001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.5441907565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……でも私のことは気にしなくていいから\nさくらちゃんはお祭りを楽しんできて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you… but don't worry about me.\nYou should go and enjoy the festival‚ Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5441907565,
      "endTime": 167.75084749849998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、一緒に行くって約束したから\n友ちゃんが行かないのに私だけ行くのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we promised to go together.\nI can't go alone while you stay here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9441805839,
      "endTime": 176.3810290336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.567695872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob4",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-tomo008.m4a",
      "text": "流星群を見るのを楽しみにしてたでしょ？　お祭りの\n様子も教えて欲しいな。私のためにも行ってきて、ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were looking forward to the meteor shower‚ right?\nI want you to tell me all about it. Go for my sake too‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.567695872,
      "endTime": 187.0276990573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.2343655904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "友ちゃん……\n……分かった、星見まつりに行ってくるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomo-chan…\n…Okay‚ I'll go to the Hoshimi Festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.2343655904,
      "endTime": 196.8953179677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
